data.description: Lots of space! 5 bedroom, 1.5 bath sitting on 4 acres. Eat in kitchen with a large pantry.  First floor Laundry. Attached 1 car garage, as well as a barn for storage.  Located on a paved road just a few miles East of M-24.  This home has a lot of potential.  Come take a look!
